# dsmcp design-system governance
- Before writing UI: get_contract({ stack: "css-vars" }).
- Use only approved tokens; never hardcode colors or raw spacing/radius/shadow.
- Copy get_component_spec blueprints; cover hover/active/focus-visible/disabled in every mode (light, dark, high-contrast-dark).
- One mode strategy: data-theme. Run "npx --yes dsmcp validate ." before finishing.
